{"tid":2336282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：俄羅斯因應納瓦爾尼事件制裁歐盟多名外交官","createTime":"2020-12-22T13:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T13:11:02.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae67fa94dd777a3f6d8f9a5e5456361c5ae8987","tid":2336282,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"蛾硬起來了<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯制裁多名歐盟高級外交官，報復歐盟因應俄國反對派領袖納瓦爾尼中毒事件，制裁俄方官員，被制裁的歐盟官員將被禁止入境。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<strong>懷疑被落毒的納瓦爾尼</strong>，假扮俄羅斯聯邦安全局官員，致電給一名聲稱負責暗殺任務的俄國特工，對方供出落毒的經過。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯聯邦安全局說，<strong>有關電話會談內容是偽造，獲外國情報部門支持。</strong>克里姆林宮形容<strong>納瓦爾尼有病，幻想自己被迫害。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566664-20201222.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566664-20201222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=46995cfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566664-20201222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=835eb9a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566664-20201222.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4c11f19ecfd6983bee40535f703d27411215fa7a","tid":2336282,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"禁止入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有邊個歐盟官員會想去俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}